Tech Stack for MVP
Backend: Django + DRF
Frontend: React
Database: PostgreSQL or SQLite
Authentication: JWT
Geolocation & Mapping: Leaflet.js + GeoDjango
Optional Integration: Mock IoT data (simulated smart bins, sensors)

